    <item>
      <title>随着 Memecoins 的进一步上涨，比特币首次触及 70,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/memecoins-ether-are-outpacing-bitcoin-during-record-breaking-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币首次升至 70,000 美元，尽管交易者似乎将注意力转移到其他地方，以寻求被称为 memecoin 的边缘代币的更高回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/memecoins-ether-are-outpacing-bitcoin-during-record-breaking-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司股息引发冲击后，巴西市场成为全球最糟糕的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/brazil-markets-are-world-s-worst-as-petrobras-dividend-sends-shockwaves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国家石油巨头巴西国家石油公司(Petroleo Brasileiro SA)派发的股息低于预期，再次引发人们对政府加大对该国最大公司干预的担忧，导致巴西市场暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/brazil-markets-are-world-s-worst-as-petrobras-dividend-sends-shockwaves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着电动汽车风波加剧，特斯拉的华尔街粉丝变得神经兮兮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/tesla-s-wall-street-fans-turn-squeamish-with-ev-turmoil-mounting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司在华尔街多头中的支持正在减弱，建议投资者购买该股票的分析师比例降至 2021 年 4 月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/tesla-s-wall-street-fans-turn-squeamish-with-ev-turmoil-mounting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 13:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷市场的兴奋就像从未发生过的加息一样</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/exuberant-credit-investors-are-acting-like-the-days-of-easy-money-are-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[风险最高的全球债务正在超过更安全的固定收益资产。投资者的兴奋情绪让人回想起央行降息前的日子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/exuberant-credit-investors-are-acting-like-the-days-of-easy-money-are-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 12:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据提振对美联储六月降息的押注，两年期国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/bond-market-looks-to-jobs-data-to-validate-rate-cut-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国劳动力市场报告鼓励交易员押注美联储最早将于 6 月降息，短期国债周五上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/bond-market-looks-to-jobs-data-to-validate-rate-cut-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>700 亿美元投资者警告美联储 2024 年可能无法降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/a-70-billion-investor-prepares-for-fed-rate-hike-risk-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚 QIC Ltd. 警告称，美联储可能被迫全年维持高利率——甚至进一步提高——随着美国经济的强劲发展，这种逆向观点与全球市场的欢欣鼓舞背道而驰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/a-70-billion-investor-prepares-for-fed-rate-hike-risk-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司前首席执行官鲁尼 2023 年薪酬减少 180 万英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/ex-bp-ceo-looney-takes-1-8-million-hit-in-2023-compensation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司 (BP Plc) 前首席执行官伯纳德·鲁尼 (Bernard Looney) 去年意外辞职，2023 年的总薪酬减少了 180 万英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/ex-bp-ceo-looney-takes-1-8-million-hit-in-2023-compensation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价将迎来 2021 年以来波动最小的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于北美基斯通管道的短暂中断未能使油价摆脱多年来最紧张的每周交易区间，油价下跌。]]></description>
